theorem dense_iff_interior_closure_eq_univ {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Dense A ↔ interior (closure A) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  constructor
  · intro hDense
    exact interior_closure_eq_univ_of_dense (A := A) hDense
  · intro hInt
    -- From the given equality derive `closure A = univ`.
    have hClosure : (closure A : Set X) = Set.univ :=
      ((interior_closure_eq_univ_iff (A := A)).1) hInt
    -- Unfolding the definition of `Dense` concludes the proof.
    simpa [Dense] using hClosure

theorem frontier_closure_eq_frontier_of_closed {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} (hA : IsClosed A) :
    frontier (closure A) = frontier A := by
  simpa [hA.closure_eq]
